The Paypal link is removed. Thanks to your generosity, I have covered another couple of months bandwidth costs. Once again I am amazed at the response.</p><p>The good news is, I have booked a week off of work in september. If I havnt managed to move the site to the new location, and recode it to allow dynamic updates, so I can hire a team of reporters, by then, then I vow that I will spend that week off doing the work!</p><p>This will mean, MUCH more regular site updates, of both news and articles, a monk equipment database, and more, and hopefully cheaper costs for me to run.

