<FONT size=2 face="Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif">Submitted by <a href="mailto:zadkiel@monkly-business.com">Zadkiel</a></FONT></p>
<ul>
<FONT size=3 face="Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif" color="#8b1a1a"><p>The Donations have been very generous indeed, and I have covered my costs for the last 2 or 3 months worth of bandwidth charges, and for that I am very grateful. A MASSIVE thank you to everyone who sent me cash, no matter if it was $1 or $100. I am removing the paypal link.</p><p>Unfortunately I had a total system wipeout thanks to Anarchy Online, and I have lost a lot of data. I managed to recover most everything, but the main thing I have lost was all the 'pending' submissions to the site. If you have submitted anything in the last couple of months which has not been included on the site yet, then PLEASE resend it to me</p><p>Work on the new site coding is progressing nicely.</p></p></FONT></ul>


